00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:30,760
Kau…

380
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,590
Tunggu.

381
00:21:33,030 --> 00:21:34,350
Kau mau pergi ke mana?

382
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:35,560
Bukan urusanmu.

383
00:21:35,560 --> 00:21:37,180
Aku tahu kau sangat
marah sekarang,…

384
00:21:37,180 --> 00:21:39,800
