desa ataupun toko.

385
00:21:39,870 --> 00:21:41,800
Setidaknya biarkan aku
antar kau ke hotel dulu.

386
00:21:41,840 --> 00:21:42,390
Tidak perlu.

387
00:21:42,390 --> 00:21:43,350
Zhou Shi.

388
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:45,680
Ternyata benar kau.

389
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:46,880
Kapan kau pulang ke Tiongkok?

390
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:48,180
Aku baru pulang dua hari lalu.

391
00:21:48,180 --> 00:21:50,210
Sanggraloka di sebelah
pesan lukisan dinding.

392
00:21:50,210 --> 00:21:51,700
Kupikir mau hubungi kau
dua hari ini.

393
00:21:51,700 --> 00:21:53,320
Tidak disangka bisa
bertemu kau di sini.

394
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:57,070
Presdir Wei.

395
