hanya ada satu hotel ini?

412
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:45,110
Masih ada, tapi di kota.

413
00:22:45,110 --> 00:22:47,040
Pulang pergi butuh empat jam.

414
00:22:47,080 --> 00:22:49,070
